title: New Website
content: Welcome to the brand new website!

title: End of Season
content:
Hey there Wolverines!
 
 After the conclusion of our season at Purdue University, we voted on 2020 Executive Board positions and Team Awards. The 2020 Executive Board has been posted to the website under about us and the team awards have been added to the roster. Cheers to an unforgetable season!
